author: rcm
msg: Updated ParameterSet so it is told the context to be used for recreating the parameters.

author: rcm
msg: Started to refactor the content objects so a single view can deal with both a field object and a parameter object.  Essentially the duplicated code found in the views is now part of the Content objects.
Lookup objects are now showing as drop-down lists in dialogs.
Fixed the bug where clearing a reference in a dialog would break the whole application.

author: rcm
msg: Created a sortable internal collection - InternalCollectionSortableVector - and an interface to define the sort order.

author: rcm
msg: Added the invoke methods offered by TestObject to TestClass, allowing class methods to be tested and run.
Refactor TestObject and TestClass so that all the invoke method are provided by a superclass.

Replaced the action methods that took a single TestObject parameter with methods that take a TestNaked; now there are zero, one, and many parameter versions of each method, and each one can take a test value or object.
